<p>Follow these quick steps to understand how to get started using the Web Experience Toolkit on your own site to create <a href="index-{{language}}.html#usability">usable</a>, <a href="index-{{language}}.html#accessibility">accessible</a>, <a href="index-{{language}}.html#mobile-friendly-responsive-design">mobile-friendly websites and applications</a>. Before you get started, discover which <a href="ref/variants-{{language}}.html">variants</a> are available in the Web Experience Toolkit. Start by choosing a flexible theme. Then find the components that meet your content needs. Finally, customize display elements such as buttons and icons.</p>

